# abc.abstractmethod — iterator/sequence protocol dict-presence
#
# abc.abstractmethod is a plain Python function; its own __dict__ is empty.
# It does NOT define __iter__, __next__, __aiter__, __anext__, __await__,
# __length_hint__, __reversed__, or __missing__ in its direct __dict__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

